'''''Bathysphere''''' was an [[Action VI bulk transport/Legends|Action VI bulk transport]] owned by the [[Mon Calamari/Legends|Mon Calamari]] [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]] [[Bringe]]. Due to Bringe's condition of not being able to handle normal [[Atmosphere/Legends|atmospheric]] pressure, the cabin of ''Bathysphere'' was pressurized.

